Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 22 May 2023
Under The Dream Pty Ltd ("we", "us", "our") values your privacy and is committed to protecting the information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use our mobile application ("Spicy Chat AI", or "SPANK" in some regions).
Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information or data about you when you use our App. Any customized data you create while using the App, such as preferences, settings, or personal content, is stored exclusively in your own device and/or in your private iCloud database. We do not have access to this data, nor do we store it on our servers. The data in your iCloud database can be deleted at any time via the settings on your device.
How We Use Information
As we do not collect or have access to any of your personal information, we do not use it for any purpose.
Sharing and Disclosure of Information
We do not share or disclose any personal information, as we do not collect or have access to it.
Data Security
While we do not collect or store your personal information, we still take data security seriously. Your customized data is stored in your own private iCloud database, which employs strong security measures to protect your information. We encourage you to follow best practices for securing your iCloud account, such as using strong passwords and enabling two-factor authentication.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we will update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Under The Dream
support@underthedream.com
This website uses cookies.
We use cookies to analyze website traffic and optimize your website experience. By accepting our use of cookies, your data will be aggregated with all other user data.
